{"article_id":"sx1Ig2oZxc6m2Ier","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Hillary Clinton emerged from her showdown with the Republican-led House Benghazi Committee largely unscathed ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"fending off accusations","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that she failed to protect the four Americans","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"who died in the 2012 attack","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"- and avoiding any bombshells over her email account .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The 2016 Democratic front-runner had been eager to put the hearing in the rear view mirror ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"and her appearance at the punishing 11-hour event comes","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"as she has the wind at her back .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Last week she delivered a winning debate performance ,","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"and this week Vice President Joe Biden announced","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"he would not challenge her for the White House .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Still , the former Secretary of State faced sharp questions from Republicans about her handling of the run-up and aftermath of the attacks in Benghazi ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"which claimed the lives of Ambassador Chris Stevens and three other Americans .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"GOP lawmakers repeatedly pressed her to explain","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"why she didn ' t know about Stevens ' requests for more security .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Clinton addressed those questions with the same cool and calm demeanor","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that she kept up for the duration ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"save for some exasperated looks and a moment of levity towards the end of the day","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"when Rep. Martha Roby","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"( R-Ala. )","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"asked","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"if she was alone for the entirety of the night of the Benghazi attacks .","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Clinton laughed","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"when she confirmed","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"that she had indeed been alone all night .","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"Ultimately , Clinton said","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"security on the ground wasn ' t her job","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"- but","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"should Stevens have asked her for help ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"he would have gotten it .","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"Clinton also told the committee","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that she `` lost more sleep","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"than all of you put together '' over the Sept. 11 , 2012 attacks .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"\" I don ' t want anything","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"that is said to me or about me","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"to take away from the heroic efforts","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"that the diplomatic security officers exhibited , \"","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"Clinton said ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"before delivering a somber account of that night in Benghazi","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"when Stevens and the security officers lost their lives .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Amid all the back-and-forth over security , the lingering email scandal was the subtext for several lines of questioning ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"particularly when Republicans zeroed in on exchanges between Clinton and her long-time ally Sidney Blumenthal ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"who had encouraged her to be bold in Libya .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Republicans noted","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"while security requests from Stevens never reached her inbox ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"her old friend ' s unsubstantiated Libya intelligence and policy advice did .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"\" Help us understand how Sidney Blumenthal had that kind of access to you , Madame Secretary ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"but the ambassador did not , \"","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Benghazi Committee Chairman Trey Gowdy","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"( R-S.C. )","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"demanded .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"And at the end of the marathon day ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"after the panel had covered much of the same ground","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that previous Benghazi inquiries had","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"-- though sometimes in greater detail --","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Republicans turned more directly to the question of Clinton ' s private email server , and what they called her \" changing story \" on the matter .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Still , Gowdy seemed to suggest","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that the hearing failed to produce any major new revelations , at least at first blush .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that she testified that much differently today","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"than the previous times","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"she testified , ''","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"Gowdy said","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"after the hearing wrapped up around 9 p.m. ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"although he said","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"he would have to go back through the transcript .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"As she has done before over the past months ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Clinton stated firmly","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that \" I turned over every work-related-email in my possession , \"","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"an answer","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that left Republicans fuming .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"\" Secretary Clinton , seems like there 's a pattern , a pattern","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"of changing your story , \"","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"said Rep. Jim Jordan","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"( R-Ohio ) .","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"\" You say one thing ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"the truth comes out ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"weeks and months later , you say something else .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"That 's not being the ' most transparent person ever. '","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"That 's not even being transparent... .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"How can we accept your statement","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that you 've turned over all work related e-mails and all e-mails about Libya ? \"","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"Clinton did refuse to answer questions","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"about how her lawyers had selected","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"which emails were work-related ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"and thus needed to be sent over the State Department","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"to comply with record-keeping rules .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"She noted","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that the panel had already talked to her lawyer for \" nine hours \"","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"- and deferred to her team for specifics .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"As the day bled into evening and then night ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Clinton increasingly chided the panel .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"\" I can ' t help it","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that you don ' t like the findings of [ State ' s internal investigation of the attacks ] , \"","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"she told Gowdy .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"\" I can ' t help it that you don ' t like the findings of the other committees . \"","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Panel Democrats also proved to be a huge asset for Clinton during the hearing ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"bashing that committee as a waste of money","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that has produced no new information","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"and dismissing it as a political circus .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"\" It bothers me","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"when I hear people imply","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"you didn ' t care about your people , \"","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Ranking Democrat Elijah Cummings","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"( D-Md . )","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"said ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"as the room erupted in applause .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"\" That ' s not right....","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"I don ' t know what we want from you...","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"do we want to badger you","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"until we get the ' gotcha ' moment ?","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"We ' re better than that...","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"we are better","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"than using taxpayer dollars","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"to try to destroy a campaign . \"","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"For their part , Republicans kept hammering away at Clinton for what they said","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"was her inability","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"to grasp or get control of the deteriorating security situation in Libya .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"In a dramatic moment late in the evening , Rep. Peter Roskam","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"( R-Ill. )","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"held up a piece of paper","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"and ripped it in half","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"to demonstrate ,","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"he said ,","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"what happened to Steven ' s request for more protections .","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"\" Here ' s what is what happened to their requests , \"","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"tearing the paper in half with a loud rip .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"\" They were torn up . \"","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"But Clinton reiterated at several points","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"that no one ever told her","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"they needed to withdraw from Libya .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"\" There was never a recommendation ...","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"to shut down Benghazi","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"even after the two attacks","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"that the compound suffered , \"","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"\" And perhaps you ' d wonder why ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"but I can tell you","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"it was thought that mission in Benghazi... was vital to our national interests...","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"No one ever came to me","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"and said :","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"We should shut down our compound in Benghazi . \"","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"Gowdy called up a series of June 2012 emails","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"he says","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"show","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"State ' s Washington headquarters was not prioritizing the security needs of diplomats in the field .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"In the emails","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"- sent around the time","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"an improvised explosive device exploded outside the Benghazi compound","depth":16},{"id":152,"text":"and a rocket-propelled grenade hit the British ambassador ' s convoy ,","depth":16},{"id":153,"text":"triggering the United Kingdom to shutter its consulate -","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"Stevens requested more protection .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"At the same time , Clinton ' s top policy aide , Jake Sullivan , was emailing Stevens for his take on a Libya memo from Blumenthal ,","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"who","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"Republicans believe","depth":16},{"id":158,"text":"may have personally pushed Clinton toward an aggressive Libya posture in hopes","depth":16},{"id":159,"text":"of furthering his business interests there .","depth":16},{"id":160,"text":"Gowdy asked","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"why Blumenthal ' s emails reached her","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"but Stevens ' didn ' t .","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"Clinton said","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"Stevens could have reached out","depth":16},{"id":165,"text":"and he would have been \" immediately responded \" to","depth":16},{"id":166,"text":"-","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"but he did not .","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"\" You know ,","depth":14},{"id":169,"text":"Mr. Chairman ,","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"I ' ve said it before ,","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"I will say it again :","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"... I communicated with him about certain issues .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"He did not raise security with me , \"","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"she said .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"\" He raised the issue with security professionals .","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"Now I know","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"that ' s not the answer","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"you want to hear ...","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"but those are the facts . \"","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"Gowdy also questioned her on another email around that time from State Department spokeswoman Victoria Nuland ,","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"asking Stevens for his advice","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"on how to publicly \" message \" the violence in Libya .","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"\" Having to stop and provide public messaging advice to your [ press shop ] \" is not what Stevens needed ,","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"Gowdy said .","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"\" He didn ' t need help","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"messaging the violence .","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"He needed help actually with the violence . ''","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"The two also tussled on whether Blumenthal ' s emails were really \" unsolicited , \"","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"with Gowdy asking her","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"if she knew the definition of the word .","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"When she said","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"she did ,","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"Gowdy read a number of Clinton responses to Blumenthal ,","depth":15},{"id":194,"text":"suggesting","depth":16},{"id":195,"text":"they weren ' t unsolicited :","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"\" Another keeper , thanks","depth":16},{"id":197,"text":"and please keep them coming \"","depth":16},{"id":198,"text":"or \" any other info about it ? \"","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"Clinton then tweaked her statement slightly ,","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"saying :","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"\" They started out unsolicited . \"","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"Gowdy pounced :","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"\" You did n't say","depth":17},{"id":204,"text":"they started off unsolicited .","depth":17},{"id":205,"text":"You said","depth":17},{"id":206,"text":"they were unsolicited . \"","depth":17},{"id":207,"text":"\" Well they were unsolicited ,","depth":17},{"id":208,"text":"but obviously I did respond to some of them , \"","depth":17},{"id":209,"text":"she shot back .","depth":16},{"id":210,"text":"Clinton repeated herself a number of times for emphasis :","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"\" Sid Blumenthal was not my adviser , official or unofficial , on Libya. \"","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"But Clinton did sometimes forward on his advice and unsubstantiated intelligence to her top aides .","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"Democrats have said","depth":6},{"id":214,"text":"Blumenthal is irrelevant and an attempt by the GOP","depth":7},{"id":215,"text":"to target her political allies .","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"California Democrat Adam Schiff said","depth":7},{"id":217,"text":"the GOP is obsessed with Blumenthal and Clinton politics ,","depth":7},{"id":218,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"the GOP used the bulk of their interview with Blumenthal this spring","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"to ask questions far afield of Benghazi .","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"\" Republicans asked more than 160 questions about Mr. Blumenthal ' s relationship and communications with the Clintons","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"but less than 20 questions about the Benghazi attacks , \"","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"launching into a bunch of comparisons .","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"\" Republicans asked more than 270 questions about Mr. Blumenthal ' s alleged business activities in Libya","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"but no questions about the U.S. presence in Benghazi . \"","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"At times , Clinton appeared to get emotional ,","depth":5},{"id":228,"text":"especially when asked","depth":6},{"id":229,"text":"how it felt to be the subject of an investigation","depth":7},{"id":230,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"one Democrat said","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"indirectly blamed her for the death of Stevens and three other Americans in the attacks .","depth":8},{"id":233,"text":"\" It ' s a very personally painful accusation , \"","depth":7},{"id":234,"text":"Clinton said ,","depth":8},{"id":235,"text":"her voice shaking .","depth":8},{"id":236,"text":"\" It has been rejected and disproven by non-partisan , dispassionate investigators","depth":7},{"id":237,"text":"but , nevertheless , having it continue to be bandied around is deeply distressing to me .","depth":7},{"id":238,"text":"I would imagine","depth":6},{"id":239,"text":"I ' ve thought more about what happened","depth":8},{"id":240,"text":"than all of you put together .","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"I ' ve lost more sleep","depth":8},{"id":242,"text":"than all of you put together . \"","depth":8},{"id":243,"text":"But she fired back in kind","depth":5},{"id":244,"text":"if Republican questions got pointed .","depth":5},{"id":245,"text":"When Roskam accused Clinton of taking credit for the 2011 Libyan revolution","depth":8},{"id":246,"text":"when times were good ,","depth":8},{"id":247,"text":"but disappearing the next year","depth":8},{"id":248,"text":"when things got sour ,","depth":8},{"id":249,"text":"Clinton","depth":8},{"id":250,"text":"- looking annoyed -","depth":8},{"id":251,"text":"got the last word in .","depth":7},{"id":252,"text":"\" Well , congressman , that is only a political statement","depth":8},{"id":253,"text":"which you well understand ,","depth":8},{"id":254,"text":"and I don ' t understand","depth":8},{"id":255,"text":"what that has anything to do with what we were supposed to be talking about today , \"","depth":8},{"id":256,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":257,"text":"Before the hearing began ,","depth":7},{"id":258,"text":"the hundreds of public seats were entirely filled by people","depth":8},{"id":259,"text":"who had been in line for hours","depth":10},{"id":260,"text":"to get access to the room ,","depth":10},{"id":261,"text":"anticipating Clinton 's entrance","depth":10},{"id":262,"text":"and clamoring for pictures with smartphones .","depth":10},{"id":263,"text":"By late morning , during some of the more technical lines of questioning , many of the public seats had emptied out .","depth":7},{"id":264,"text":"Several members of the public had fallen asleep ,","depth":8},{"id":265,"text":"and former Rep. Tom Davis ,","depth":10},{"id":266,"text":"seated in the front row of the public seating ,","depth":10},{"id":267,"text":"had his eyes closed","depth":10},{"id":268,"text":"and hand over his head .","depth":10},{"id":269,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":270,"text":"while the audience may have been bored ,","depth":7},{"id":271,"text":"there were several tense moments","depth":8},{"id":272,"text":"when Clinton faced off with Republicans","depth":8},{"id":273,"text":"- or when the Democrats jumped in","depth":8},{"id":274,"text":"to defend her .","depth":8},{"id":275,"text":"Cummings blasted the committee as a partisan witch hunt","depth":7},{"id":276,"text":"out to get Clinton ,","depth":7},{"id":277,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":278,"text":"Republicans formed the panel","depth":9},{"id":279,"text":"because they \" did not like the answers","depth":11},{"id":280,"text":"they got \" in previous probes -","depth":11},{"id":281,"text":"\" so they set up this select committee with no rules , no deadlines and an unlimited budget . \"","depth":10},{"id":282,"text":"\" They set them loose","depth":10},{"id":283,"text":"because you ' re running for president , \"","depth":10},{"id":284,"text":"Cummings said ,","depth":10},{"id":285,"text":"raising his voice","depth":10},{"id":286,"text":"before calling for the panel to disband .","depth":9},{"id":287,"text":"\" It is time for Republicans to end this ... fishing expedition . \"","depth":9},{"id":288,"text":"It took Cummings only a few minutes into the hearing to highlight a number of embarrassing moments for Gowdy in recent weeks ,","depth":7},{"id":289,"text":"including comments by Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy","depth":11},{"id":290,"text":"( R-Calif. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":291,"text":"Rep. Richard Hanna","depth":12},{"id":292,"text":"( R-N.Y. )","depth":12},{"id":293,"text":"and a fired GOP Benghazi investigator","depth":11},{"id":294,"text":"who all suggested","depth":9},{"id":295,"text":"the panel was either out to hurt Clinton","depth":9},{"id":296,"text":"or increasingly focused on investigating her .","depth":9},{"id":297,"text":"Gowdy","depth":10},{"id":298,"text":"- who opened the hearing","depth":11},{"id":299,"text":"by responding to recent criticism","depth":12},{"id":300,"text":"that his panel is a waste of taxpayer money -","depth":12},{"id":301,"text":"assured Clinton","depth":9},{"id":302,"text":"that was not the case .","depth":8},{"id":303,"text":"He pushed back against recent claims","depth":9},{"id":304,"text":"that his panel is just a re-tread of a half-dozen committee investigations and State ' s own internal investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":305,"text":"calling them too \" narrow \" and \" not thorough . \"","depth":8},{"id":306,"text":"Still , though , Republicans failed to produce a palpable hit , particularly on the email question .","depth":4},{"id":307,"text":"Rep. Susan Brooks","depth":11},{"id":308,"text":"( R-Indiana ) ,","depth":11},{"id":309,"text":"at one point , pulled out a large stack of Clinton emails on Libya in 2011","depth":10},{"id":310,"text":"and compared them to a much smaller stack from 2012 ,","depth":9},{"id":311,"text":"pressing Clinton on why she wasn ' t getting more updates on the worsening security situation in Libya in 2012 .","depth":8},{"id":312,"text":"\" I can only conclude by your own records","depth":10},{"id":313,"text":"that there was a lack of interest in Libya in 2012 , \"","depth":10},{"id":314,"text":"Brooks said ,","depth":9},{"id":315,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":316,"text":"that there were no Clinton emails about two attacks on the Benghazi mission","depth":10},{"id":317,"text":"that happened in April and then June of 2012 .","depth":10},{"id":318,"text":"\" There was a lot of communication to you or from you in 2011 ,","depth":8},{"id":319,"text":"and that is when","depth":9},{"id":320,"text":"[ Libyan leader Muammar Qadhafi ] fell ,","depth":9},{"id":321,"text":"but then","depth":9},{"id":322,"text":"when we go to 2012 , Libya , Benghazi , Chris Stevens ,","depth":10},{"id":323,"text":"they seem to fall off your radar -","depth":10},{"id":324,"text":"but it was getting much worse . \"","depth":8},{"id":325,"text":"Clinton noted","depth":8},{"id":326,"text":"that email was not her primary mode of communicating ,","depth":8},{"id":327,"text":"so they didn ' t show the full picture","depth":8},{"id":328,"text":"of how often she was getting briefed :","depth":8},{"id":329,"text":"\" Most of my work was not done on emails with my closest aides , with officials in the State Department , officials in the rest of the government as well as the White House and people around the world , \"","depth":7},{"id":330,"text":"she explained .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":661,"left":557,"right":660,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":557,"left":370,"right":556,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":370,"left":338,"right":369,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":338,"left":335,"right":337,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":335,"left":0,"right":334,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":334,"left